item.title: Graphical computation
item.description: This is an interdisciplinary project where there are several macros programmed in visual basic for applications, where it manages automated responses of e-mail, generation of graphic files in inventor, invoices and quotations in microsoft word and management of a database in mysql. https://github.com/dicrojasch/ComputacionGrafica
